descp2: A `Tensor`. Must be one of the following types: `int32`, `int64`. Dimension must be 0-D or 1-D. `shift[i]` specifies the number of places by which elements are shifted positively (towards larger indices) along the dimension specified by `axis[i]`. Negative shifts will roll the elements in the opposite direction.
